{"tid":810578,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【百載繁榮一夢消？】清朝光緒山西省五台山落魄道人對香港預言！","createTime":"2018-09-08T05:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T04:10:51.000Z","uid":173631,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"684b90b58eed812f2a2580acc62efccff8137524","tid":810578,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.i-ching.com.hk/web/?p=121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.i-ching.com.hk%2Fweb%2F%3Fp%3D121&d=f5gKr6U84mP3KOVxb21sgosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=a615a92f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.i-ching.com.hk/web/?p=121</a><br />\n(6月10日)重讀我的資料庫，看到收藏的一段百年預測，不覺深有所感，發表於此，以饗讀者：<br />\n <br />\n一百零五年前，曾經有一位山西五臺山的落魄道人，在全國遊歷後由桂入粵而抵香江，在太平山頂眺望後，寫下兩首七言絕詩，<br />\n第一首曰：<br />\n層樓高聳插漢霄，<br />\n車水馬龍沓沓囂；<br />\n鯉魚有日翻洋海，<br />\n百載繁華一夢消。<br />\n第二首曰：<br />\n直上太平望眼高，<br />\n天翻地動落玄毛；<br />\n太惜丑牛乘乙木，<br />\n不堪回首問洪濤。<br />\n詩中隱藏香港之玄機，看誰能夠勘破。(明續)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/135001_3626850d481efd38a8ae8164011f41b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F135001_3626850d481efd38a8ae8164011f41b2.jpg&h=dda9f4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/135001_4c62292248e11cd381a6a8cc85cf2506.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F135001_4c62292248e11cd381a6a8cc85cf2506.jpg&h=76c48d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/135001_4527c4531c7ed6549feef9f10fb066d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F135001_4527c4531c7ed6549feef9f10fb066d1.jpg&h=33cfe241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/135002_531b4440725da7f145e48b006cae0955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3