/>\n靈龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n太惜丑牛乘乙木，<br />\n不堪回首問洪濤。<br />\n呢兩句好精妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2dac4e3a855a7b9f8a6d45bad2f31bed6047709","tid":810578,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"山竹唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}